channel.title: Ip for a private server (PLEASE READ)
channel.description:
Hi, I've been trying to get a static ip for an no-ip server 4 a while. My comp just doesn't do the command ipconfig so I can't get the static ip. Is there another ip service that does not require a static ip besides hamachi. Please let me know, thanks. :)
P.S. I use windows vista if that matters.
